member.remarks:
Password must meet the following criteria: - Minimum length is 6 characters. - Must contain at least one numeric digit ('0'-'9'). - Must contain at least one lowercase character ('a'-'z'). - Must contain at least one uppercase character ('A'-'Z'). - Must contain at least one non-alphanumeric character (e.g., '!', '@', '#', etc.).
Sample request:
POST /api/User/Register { "email": "user@example.com", "firstName": "John", "lastName": "Doe", "password": "Password123!", "balance": 100.00 }
